WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
  background-image: black;
  font-family: 'Permanent Marker', Lora, monospace;
  color: cadetblue;
  line: 1;
  align: left;
}

1
00:00:22.136 --> 00:00:24.136
Another day,

2
00:00:24.386 --> 00:00:26.386
I'm all alone.

3
00:00:26.903 --> 00:00:28.903
I wonder what to do again.

4
00:00:31.497 --> 00:00:33.497
I take a seat,

5
00:00:33.284 --> 00:00:35.284
then I endure

6
00:00:35.534 --> 00:00:40.534
cascading flows of thoughts,

7
00:00:40.566 --> 00:00:42.566
and so I freeze again,

8
00:00:42.576 --> 00:00:44.576
paralyzed,

9
00:00:44.606 --> 00:00:48.606
directionless and overwhelmed,

10
00:00:49.158 --> 00:00:51.158
I close my eyes,

11
00:00:51.659 --> 00:00:55.659
fostering the will to take my leave.